import Textbox from "../components/Textbox"
import Imagebox from "../components/Imagebox"

const sectionStyle = {
  padding: '20px',
  boxSizing: 'border-box',
  display: 'flex',
  alignItems: 'center',
  justifyContent: 'center',
  flexDirection: 'row',
  height: '77vh',
  gap: '20px'
}

const Objects = ({ output, image, objectClass }) => {
  return <>
    <section style={sectionStyle}>
      <Textbox title={'output'} text={output} />
      <Imagebox objectClass={objectClass} image={image} />
    </section>
  </>
}

export default Objects
